node.text:
Rhea the rescued bird! 🐥
Video by: @rhea_thenakedbirdie
Rhea is a 2 year old lovebird with a Beak & Feather Disease which causes her feathers to fall off. She’s still a beautiful, happy bird, who loves to sing ❤️
Explore. Share. Inspire: #earthfocus
